Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打败木偶兽的孩子们 再度踏入另一个新的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而小光却因为发烧卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一等人外出四处寻找感冒药
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却遇到了黑暗四天王之中的 第三位杀手机械邪龙兽狂风暴雨似的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们躲过一劫 以为可以再见到小光的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限大炮爆炸的威力把太一等人震落到了深渊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四十九话「再见 鼻涕兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒过来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿岳 迪路兽 我怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在感觉如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像已经退了 现在觉得身体舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你刚才昏睡了很久 不过好像对你的身体反而有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人去哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他们找到谁了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小光 太好了 你终于醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一他们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许太一和光子郎他们掉到别的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个 这个是比丘兽找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你生病了 太一他们好不容易才找到感冒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的路就像是一个迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我们一起出去找 一定可以找到到他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也一定会努力去找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是他的妹妹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现实世界的地底下?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空也这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上面是现实世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点 你们有没有听到什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧? 不知道是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好像是从那边传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点转! 认真工作! 不许有人偷懒!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些见不得阳光又没有用的鼻涕兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是机械邪龙兽大王所控制的 黑暗龙卷山上巨大城市的动力和能源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点工作吧! 一直工作到死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是熊仔兽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是熊仔兽 是恶霸熊仔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶霸熊仔兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶霸熊仔兽 虽然和熊仔兽长得有点相像 但它长相非常凶恶可怕的玩具型数码宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的个性就如名字一样 绝招是「心碎一击」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也是机械邪龙兽的部下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它也是机械帝国军团的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么? 还不快点给我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽好可怜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么? 快工作!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 看你们往哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路兽 我没事 你不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让鼻涕兽们恢复自由 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追得到我们你就来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些小鬼 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丘兽进化…巴多拉兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴达兽进化…天使兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是能量不足吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只好溜之大吉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 你看我在飞 我从来没有飞得这么快过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿岳 我也是 我飞得好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个逃命逃到脱离现实了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽们在呼喊着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽 你们在这里干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么? 这种眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 是谁把鼻涕兽身上的链子给打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开锁的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去保护小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你们想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去保护小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是输给鼻涕兽我就不叫做恶霸熊仔兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这是什么光芒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体里面充满能量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得能量多到快要溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪路兽超进化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丘兽进化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴多拉兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴达兽进化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想、想打架是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就连你们一起收拾掉 看我的厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石巨翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽 你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕 鼻涕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个样子 你应该很快就会好起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是代表小光的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光芒会带领我们前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们只要跟着光往前走就可以找到太一他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 就把我们要走的路交给你的光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽大王 机械邪龙兽大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恶霸熊仔兽吗? 什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个被选召的孩子和他们的数码宝贝来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在你的管辖区域里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要讨机械邪龙兽大王的欢心 我很勇敢地和他们战斗 可是还是被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你发现那几个小鬼的行踪 竟然没有通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才跟那几个小鬼的数码宝贝战斗的时候受了点伤 伤口好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽大王 求求你救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那几个小鬼在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再留着你也没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚古兽 你在干什么? 快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 亚古兽和甲虫兽都已经很累了 我们先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的 我也累得快撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 你冷静一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你也一定累得快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光…她在发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我们都知道小光生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道 那你就不要指使我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太、太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指使你? 我什么时候指使你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再烦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你简直不明事理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都冷静一点好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有谁跟在我们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们躲在门口面 然后假装还在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然真的动手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打你又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是机械邪龙兽的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫兽进化…比多兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚古兽进化…暴龙兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴龙兽…暴龙兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚古兽 你们应该是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我知道你真的很担心小光的病才会这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要负起责任 我去战斗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们同心协力 一定有办法打败它们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽 曾经在文件岛见过的改造人型数码宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次因为比多兽帮忙 取出身上的黑色齿轮才得以解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有想到居然会是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才没想到是你呢 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 安杜路兽 你在这个地方做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我躲在机械邪龙兽所控制的城市底下从事反抗活动 我希望能够解救那些被暴力所控制的数码宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我还以为你们几个是机械邪龙兽的部下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找一个名字叫做小光的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我猜测 阿空和阿岳也跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 请你们稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你帮帮忙 小光是太一的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光要来这个地方了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里呀 被选召的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽也在这里 正好可以把你们一次解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点先找一个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说太一他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿空 阿岳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光\N光子郎 甲虫兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽跟你们发生冲突了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安杜路兽为了保护我们正在跟它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说它在地底下从事反抗活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石巨翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋转能量剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械邪龙兽是究极体数码宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不堪一击的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就轮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 尽是一些老弱残兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也想跟我战斗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕兽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体…充满了能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚古兽究极进化…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗暴龙兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 振作一点 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚球兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我还有太一和小光 大家都跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不——!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的控制者机械邪龙兽被打败了 这个地区也要开始崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心 有我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里恐怕也岌岌可危了 大家赶快离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市消失了 我的任务也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 等我们到地面去 为鼻涕兽它们做个坟墓好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着吧 小丑皇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一等人好不容易到了黑暗龙卷山的山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却遇上另外一只可怕的数码宝贝妖女兽的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女兽上前抵挡 与她战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场光明与黑暗之女的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回数码宝贝大冒险\N「女性对决 妖女兽!」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 冒险越来越深入了